      "content": "idk i feel like i've had panic attacks before and this feels kinda similar... just really intense. but the breathing thing feels like it's not doing much for the sharp pain. do u think if i just take some extra melatonin or maybe a mild sedative i can just sleep it off? i really dont want to go to a hospital in a random country if i dont have to lol",
